Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two were really alone\Nbefore they came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When they were taken into custody\Nnear the border of Czechoslovakia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they were holding hands\Nas they walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They both were shivering in the cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the conditions of the\Norphanages in the east side were horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not like 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Inge, the bathroom isn't that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's all right...\NThere's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... you can go to the bathroom\Nby yourself, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids really did not know\Na parent's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You only need love in order to\Ndevelop as a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As you say, the orphanages\Nof the east side were quite horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this place was once referred to\Nas Orphanage 47.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we did what we could so\Nwe wouldn't be controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by the government,\Neven just a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to avoid\Nbecoming like 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a special orphanage\Nrun by both
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ministry of Health and Welfare\Nand the Ministry of the Interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The real state of affairs\Nwere being managed by
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ministry of the Interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That place was... Old East Germany's\Nexperimental laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:35.98,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}A Little Experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Experimental laboratory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They were running a project\Nthat would turn the children
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,into perfect soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychological reconstruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Research on modifying humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They made the orphans\Njoin factions and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,observed as they fought each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an experiment to create cold,\Nmerciless humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine what these children\Nwould be like when they grew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, there's no way to prove\Nthat was happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All the data was burned\Nright before the Wall came down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The people from\Nthe Ministry of the Interior
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,who were involved with\Nthe Project escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard there is one person\Nwho was able to gloss his record
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and remain in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the person\Nwho was overseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the devilish project\Nthat was 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He was actually\Na pediatric psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,affiliated with\Nthe Ministry of the Interior...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Officially, he was a district official from\Nthe Ministry of Health and Welfare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,District official from\Nthe Ministry of Health and Welfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Inge, are you done\Nusing the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Sweet dreams. Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of that was covered up\Nby that incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That... incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened at 511 Kinderheim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I've talked\Na little too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me remember\Nsuch awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please tell me what\Nhappened there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my...\NWhere's my soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.\NIt's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold off on soccer\Nuntil your wounds have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That man said he was going to come\Nto pick you up soon, so rest until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what really happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The East German government at\Nthe time placed a strict gag order on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began with the mysterious death\Nof the director of 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, there was\Na power struggle among
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the instructors over\Nthe director's position...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage was\Nthrown into anarchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The children's internal strife\Ncouldn't be controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that Johan\Nmade it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And?! What happened to\N511 Kinderheim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All the members of the orphanage,\Nincluding the instructors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,killed each other off in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a big lie that the world is dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow will be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hartmann, aren't we going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No... let's take a detour...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't want to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, you're a good boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to hand over Dieter\Nuntil I returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That person\Nwas that child's foster parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also quite the gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Much more of a gentleman\Nthan you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, that boy\Nwanted to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hartmann's study?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that they were\Ntaken at different times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but were all taken at the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the man in the photo with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... All the photographs\Nwere taken at 511 Kinderheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten years ago up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the members of the orphanage,\Nincluding the instructors,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}killed each other off in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, hold on! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that this boy can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy can't see what Johan saw\Nfrom here back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good... It's no good again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy isn't Johan either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... Everyone died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The instructors and the orphans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All fifty of them died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan... watched it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He watched it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan... just watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"What...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He replied...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"I just dropped\Na piece of oil-soaked cloth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in into the fire like this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hatred is created\Nwhen people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just poured a little oil on it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy, just 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And he pulled it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He had fifty people kill each other\Nwithout moving a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your experiments turned him into\Nthat kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim was indeed\Nan experimental ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a project to raise orphans\Nto become perfect soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back on it now,\Nit was such a small experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about Johan?\NHim, a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a born leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He was someone who was\Nmeant to stand at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could create\Nsuch a work of art!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He was superhuman\Nfrom the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a monstrous being!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He foretold that everyone would\Nend up hating and killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think Johan's goal was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"To be the last person remaining\Nin this world..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter... The future is dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to become even just\Na little more like Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:17:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you be like Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot you if you\Nharm him any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about Johan,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nonce you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's impossible to\Nfind and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you one piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, once you hear it,\Nleave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for General Wolf. He's the one\Nwho first discovered Johan's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the man from the photograph\Nin your study?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the man in the photograph\Nwith Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who brought Johan to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He should know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide for yourself if you're\Ncoming down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot Hartmann if he puts\Nhis finger on the rifle's trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide for yourself!\NMake your own decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd leave me,\Nwould you... Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're my child...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... it's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good... Slowly... Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter... come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that you can live\Nwithout me, Dieter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hartmann! If you move,\NI'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma told me that tomorrow\Nwill be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the bus here and get off\Nat Keunen Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanage is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this to Elna Tyce...\NShe's an instructor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks scary,\Nbut she's a very nice lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We part ways here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A bus will come\Nin two or three minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that you\Ncan't come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't... come with me...
